text: Kumlekul () is a rural locality (a selo) in Krasnoyarsky Selsoviet, Ufimsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 748 as of 2010. There are 14 streets. == Geography == It is located 33 km from Ufa, 10 km from Krasny Yar. == References == Category:Rural localities in Ufimsky District
title: Kumlekul
